text:<p>英文版：Big data is like teenage sex: everyone talks about it, nobody really knows how to do it, everyone thinks everyone else is doing it, so everyone claims they are doing it. 文言文版：谈者众，明者鲜；疑人皆为之，故佯称为之。大数据者，此之谓也。感谢 <a href="http://weibo.com/thehiddendepth" target="_blank">@脱线波</a>、<a href="http://weibo.com/tbjm" target="_blank">@剑魔伯虎</a> 的分享。</p>
